Package com.project.moviebooking.service

package com.project.moviebooking.service
The "service" package contains service interfaces and implementations responsible for implementing business logic and orchestrating operations within the movie booking application.

Service interfaces and classes in this package define and implement the core business logic, handle business rules, and coordinate the interactions between controllers, repositories, and other components. These services encapsulate application-specific functionalities and facilitate the execution of operations related to movie booking.

Organizing services in this package helps maintain a structured and modular architecture, promoting separation of concerns and facilitating the implementation and management of business rules and logic within the movie booking system.
